{"tid":1584734,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人唔應該只係理自己","createTime":"2019-09-21T09:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T11:57:03.000Z","uid":299119,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"746da11ac772736ea7acfb4c16eeb6b99013a793","tid":1584734,"uid":299119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">而家先醒起今次會唔會蠢咗... 香港今次應該響應全世界, 向警務處申請climate protest. <br />\n<br />\n如果警務處唔批嘅話, 即係等於同全世界講, 香港再唔係國際文明都市. <br />\n<br />\n況且climate 議題, 真係關香港人事, 好應該響應!<br />\n<br />\n仲有新彊集中營, 維權律師, 全球性social big data 監察, 全球傳媒, 互聯網假新聞議題等等. 都香港人都應該出分力. <br />\n而家外國幫香港, 香港人都務必要加入世界行列, 面對世界社會問題.</span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"986a3618c17fa7d4f79a7f14661d13a8fee42d53","tid":1584734,"uid":299119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be40ac0a895c65bd616244e41aadb46210a65341","tid":1584734,"uid":299119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de9bd85569dc313d3a57c287d91983d9947f276","tid":1584734,"uid":299119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023ce742bb0bea36d7fdbc9b4be6c09c7b08935a","tid":1584734,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"4a2329675bb1fd61f91759d1d1fbeb9bd97962e6","tid":1584734,"uid":299119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:40:0